<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_ee11a153-c3ed-4b60-8fc3-717c684b9c31" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>B1D2</sptc><title id="_d555aba6-db8e-4ec7-8b01-77db77d95917">Resistance to actions</title><archive-num>2019: B1.1</archive-num><subclause id="_58ba0686-5d1f-4511-99fd-619859544209" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7c593830-e095-4d78-856d-6a93e9d3a1f0">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The resistance of a building or structure must be greater than the most critical action effect resulting from different combinations of actions, where—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_1f790f54-6905-481a-8556-6672e0a54e78">the most critical action effect on a building or structure is determined in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1137_1.54.0.xml#_a2a51c5c-1f14-46e7-a85f-4ddab6440278" id="_29f21f36-d765-4d6d-9c77-9d6c26865bb5" scope="local" type="clause">B1D3</xref> and the general design procedures contained in AS/NZS 1170.0; and</li><li id="_97b75702-28f2-4e3e-a765-88a3f655f3e5">design for the actions in (a) accommodates expected 10-year deflection for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/9501_0.4.0.xml#_d3cc1a16-8ec1-4c83-9d06-a8c057409202" id="_e2d4e38d-e198-4785-81c9-b0017bdabf53" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">structural substrates</xref> in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/48_0.41.0.xml#_184bf2f3-68d1-4138-809d-f42b0e8acd16" id="_43a6c222-75c6-4b3a-a56a-fee302df1c22" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-part">Part F1</xref>; and</li><li id="_65f5c8e1-bfc3-4005-a06f-46a797780966">the resistance of a building or structure is determined in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1138_1.20.0.xml#_2454b5b6-4146-468a-9ddb-dfb917ed0cda" id="_1663e1c0-9df8-4c44-b842-8db37689edd8" scope="local" type="clause">B1D4</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>